Main function of collecting articles in Ivory Coast

ci_news_collect.Rd

Collection function of all the articles of Ivory Coast

ci_news_collect(start_d, end_d, press = "all")

Arguments

start_d

yyyy-mm-dd start date of collection (oldest date, eg: yesterday)
end_d

yyyy-mm-dd end date of collection (newest date, eg: today)
press

specify the name of a press.

Value

a table containing the articles published in the period

Examples

library(afnews)
article <- ci_news_collect(start_d="2020-10-20", end_d="2020-10-25", press="all")
